casebody.data:
Monday, March 11, 2002

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

01-827. State ex rel. Moore v. Butler Cty. Court of Common Pleas.

In Mandamus. This cause came on for further consideration upon relator’s request for findings of fact/conclusions of law. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the request for findings of fact/conclusions of law be, and hereby is, denied.
